在[[酒店业|酒店业]]，'''夜床服务'''（'''开夜床'''）是指酒店员工将宾客[[床|床]]的床上用品翻开，以备宾客睡眠使用的行为。<ref name="HotelChatter - 8Jul2011 - Our Set List for the Ultimate Hotel Turndown Service">{{Citation|url = http://www.hotelchatter.com/story/2011/7/8/101823/9440/hotels/Our_Set_List_for_the_Ultimate_Hotel_Turndown_Service|title = Our Set List for the Ultimate Hotel Turndown Service|last = Shallcross|first = Juliana|date = July 8, 2011|access-date = 1 Jan 2014|archive-date = 2015-09-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924031430/http://www.hotelchatter.com/story/2011/7/8/101823/9440/hotels/Our_Set_List_for_the_Ultimate_Hotel_Turndown_Service}}</ref> 在开过夜床的[[枕头|枕头]]上，一般会放置一些[[甜点|甜点]]，例如巧克力或薄荷糖。

一些酒店还会提供更精致的夜床服务，例如为孩子提供睡前故事，为年轻夫妇提供[[鸡尾酒|鸡尾酒]]等。<ref name="The Huffington Post - 18Dec2012 - 7 Hotels With Extraordinary Nightly Turndown Services">{{Cite news|url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/the-daily-meal/hotel-turndown-service_b_2295845.html|title = 7 Hotels With Extraordinary Nightly Turndown Services|last = Mack|first = Lauren|date = December 18, 2012|work = [[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|accessdate = 7 May 2013|archive-date = 2017-08-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170829064847/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/the-daily-meal/hotel-turndown-service_b_2295845.html}}</ref>

